<div class='the_facts'>In 2013, less than 1% of our customers returned their photograph(s).</div>

<h2><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Free Return Shipping</h2>

  <p>If you are still undecided on purchasing a photograph, the odds are on your side.  If for any reason you are not 100% satisfied, you can <span class='dotted_highlight'>return any photograph free of charge</span>.  You will also get a <span class='dotted_highlight'>full refund which includes the cost of initial shipping</span>.</p>

<h2><i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></i> 14 Day Return Policy</h2>

<p>Please notify us within 14 calendar days (not business days) of when you received the package and we will send you a free return shipping label.  You will be ineligible for free return shipping if we are contacted past that time period.  </p>

<h2 class='return_divider'><i class="fa fa-tasks"></i>     Instructions For A Return</h2>
