<p class='fixit'>Once we receive your return request we will send you another email with a UPS return shipping label which you can then place on the top of your return package.</p>

<h2><i class="fa fa-dropbox"></i> Return Packaging</h2>
<p>Please package the photograph(s) back up in the same (if not similar) fashion as how they were original sent to you.  Use as much cardboard and/or insulation as possible.  Also, if shipping back a framed photo, please use the cardboard corners which came with the print.</p>

<p>Unfortunately, we will not be able to credit you for the extra packaging materials such as a new box, bubble wrap, cardboard etc.   However, we will pay for the entire UPS return shipping fee when the package gets sent back to our warehouse.</p>

